\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line PC Training and Business College is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training as a private higher education provider and is accredited to offer higher education programmes by the HEQC.\line \line The Diploma in Business Administration programme was tabled at the Accreditation Commitee meeting of 05 and 06 October 2011 and it was deferred. The institution was requested to provide clarification on the following\'3A\line \line 1. The institution must clarify and correct inconsistencies in the programme design related to levels and credits of certain modules.\line 2. Course outlines are inadequate. The lack of detail makes it difficult to determine the level and depth of the modules.\line 3. More information on the academic qualifications and experience of the programme managers is required.\line 4. There is insufficient information for a distance education evaluation. Table 1.5 which denotes learning activities cannot have the same time accorded for independent self-study for both distance and contact. \cell \pard 

